title: Raccoon tries to steal a kayaker's food
text: Intelligent and curious creatures, raccoons are known for their boldness. And this cheeky mammal certainly didn't hold back when it smelled food on a woman's surf board. The woman was paddling down a river in North America with some friends when the daring raccoon approached in the shallows. The woman was paddling down a river in North America with some friends when the daring raccoon approached in the shallows Suddenly it hopped on to her board and tried to dig its nose into her belongings, as the woman screamed in shock and jumped off her board Suddenly it hopped on to her board and tried to dig its nose into her belongings, as the woman screamed in shock and jumped off her board.
